{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e0a37a3939","title":"给臧克家的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9e38d45671","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"e0a37a3939"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji7","name":"毛泽东文集第七卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji7.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji7":{"comments":[{"id":"5602224722","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"臧克家，一九○五年生，山东诸城人。当时任中国作家协会书记处书记、《诗刊》主编。"}],"contents":[{"id":"12de435de4","type":"title","text":"给臧克家的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"5602224722","type":"appellation","text":"克家同志和各位同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"bd4db24b35","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书早已收到，迟复为歉！遵嘱将记得起来的旧体诗词，连同你们寄来的八首，一共十八首，抄寄如另纸，请加审处。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"a2884a791b","type":"paragraph","text":"这些东西，我历来不愿意正式发表，因为是旧体，怕谬种流传，贻误青年；再则诗味不多，没有什么特色。既然你们以为可以刊载，又可为已经传抄的几首改正错字，那末，就照你们的意见办吧。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"0570ca9642","type":"paragraph","text":"《诗刊》出版，很好，祝它成长发展。诗当然应以新诗为主体，旧诗可以写一些，但是不宜在青年中提倡，因为这种体裁束缚思想，又不易学。这些话仅供你们参考。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"b929eeb885","type":"paragraph","text":"同志的敬礼！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"848deb80e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"44335dc817","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年一月十二日","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"d52a583a49","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"},{"id":"8b65175a40","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939"}],"page":{"id":"dae8810139","publicationId":"wenji7","articleId":"e0a37a3939","start":193,"end":193}}}},"__N_SSG":true}